cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is about regularization techniques for neural networks, which is a topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the application of the proposed method to image recognition and point cloud recognition, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The use of projection matrices and dimensionality reduction techniques suggests that it may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the theoretical insights provided in the paper suggest that it may also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
